  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      serum levels Ca, P, PTH and vitamin D metabolites before and after treatment with
      isotretinoin for sever acne
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      few studies has been done of serum levels Ca, P, PTH and vitamin D metabolites in patients
      receiving isotretinoin .In this study we measured serum levels Ca, P, PTH and vitamin D
      metabolites before and after treatment with isotretinoin for sever acne in 30 patients . the
      patients had no kown skeletal, endocrine ,renal and gastrointestinal disorders.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
